para.text:
        Exceptions are now built-in:
          // XP1
try(); {
  // whatever
} if (catch('Exception', $e)) {
  $e->printStackTrace();
  exit();
} 

// XP2
try {
  // whatever
} catch (Exception $e) {
  $e->printStackTrace();
  exit();
}

        Dereferencing allows nicer syntax like this:
          // XP1
$l= &Logger::getInstance();
$cat= &$l->getCategory();

// XP2
$cat= Logger::getInstance()->getCategory();
